RTML Transfer Util beta 1

Jeremy Woertink (2008)
  http://www.webstoredesigner.com/
  http://www.venturawebdesign.com/

******
Requiements:

  Yahoo! Small Business account
  http://smallbusiness.yahoo.com/

  Mechanize < 0.9.0
  Nokogiri

******
Purpose:

  Find all custom RTML templates from a specified Yahoo! store.
  Saves all templates as .rtml

******
Issues:

  Currently only works on Windows Vista
  Xpath issues on Mac.
  Only downloads templates on some stores.
  Doesn't handle errors that well.

